summary: So what I got from the episodes descriptions is that: In “Hammer Time“ Andi is going to spent the whole episode releasing her...
body:
So what I got from the episodes descriptions is that:

  • In “Hammer Time“ Andi is going to spent the whole episode releasing her anger about Bex and Bowie cancelling the wedding.
  • In “Unloading Zone” Bex is going to spent the whole episode apologizing to Celia for cancelling the wedding and making her do all the wedding planning job for nothing.
  • And then in “One Girl’s Trash” Bowie is going to be like “I actually do wanna get married” and then Bex and Bowie are going to decide to get married after all, making the 2 previous storylines unnecessary and pointless.

Am I the only one that has an issue with this? Is like the Buffy moving storyline all over again! I’m so done with this wedding drama.

summary: I made post 3X13 spotify playlists from Cyrus's and TJ's point of view. Cyrus’s playlist is kind of a typical post breakup...
caption:
I made post 3X13 spotify playlists from Cyrus’s and TJ’s point of view.

Cyrus’s playlist is kind of a typical post breakup playlist. A lot of the songs that I chose for it are very fuck-you-esque and have a lot of anger, hurt, and resentment to them.  While I don’t think that Cyrus will stop talking to TJ nor do I think that this was the end of his feelings for TJ, I think that he has every right to be mad/angry/hurt at TJ and I think it’s completely understandable for Cyrus to listen to these songs.

TJ’s Playlist on the other hand is him being sad that he hurt Cyrus and being very confused about his feelings for the boy.  It starts off with him being very confused about his feeling and then slowly evolves into him realizing that he likes Cyrus and wants to be around him all the time. Though he might not necessarily be in love with Cyrus, he just knows that he can’t stand being away from him.

Cyrus’s Playlist: Fuck Feelings - Olivia O'Brien // Fighter - Christina Aguilera // 7 Rings - Ariana Grande // Dear No One - Tori Kelly // Sorry Not Sorry - Demi Lovato // Complicated - Avril Lavigne // Weight in Gold - Gallant // Gotta Go My Own Way - Zac Efron, Vanessa Hudgens (High School Musical 2) // My Happy Ending - Avril Lavigne // Maybe This Time - Liza Minnelli (Cabaret) // Gives You Hell - All American Rejects // Drink About - Seeb, Dagny // Set It All Free - Scarlett Johansson (Sing)

TJ’s Playlist: Dazed and Confused - Ruel // Maybe It Was Me - Sody // Honey - Johnny Balik // C’est La Vie - Maurice Moore // Bleeding Love - Leona Lewis // Absolutely (Story of a Girl) - Nine Days // Come Clean - Hilary Duff // Shed a Light - Robin Schulz, David Guetta, Cheat Codes // Stay With Me - Sam Smith // No Air (feat. Chris Brown) - Jordan Sparks, Chris Brown // Hold My Hand - Jess Glynne // Beautiful Soul - Jesse McCartney // I Want you Back - The Jackson 5 // Rather Be (feat. Jess Glynne) - Clean Bandit, Jess Glynne

Gifs from: @stephadoodles @bambikippen

TJ’s Playlist on the other hand is him being sad that he hurt Cyrus and being very confused about his feelings for the boy.  It starts off with him being very confused about his feeling and then slowly evolves into him realizing that he likes Cyrus and wants to be around him all the time. Though he might not necessarily be in love with Cyrus, he just knows that he can’t stand being away from him.
